<td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Where to hunt on Kunark?</span><hr size=1> I saw one message about hunting in The Overthere.  Is that that the best place?  I am currently a lvl21 mage on Terris Thule.<br>
<br>
Regards,<br>
Zor <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umezlothemage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mezlo the Mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#333333>(10/10/00 9:06:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt on Kunark?</span><hr size=1> Lake of Ill Omen - around the Sarnak fort, windmill and skeleton ruins.  Only bad part is no real place to run to when things go bad.  You can sell in the windmill to the dwarf that is there.<br>
<br>
 <p>Mezlo, Mage of 29 seasons, Torvonnilous</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzorryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zorryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#333333>(10/11/00 7:56:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt on Kunark?</span><hr size=1> I have been hunting near the windmill.  Doing pretty good so far (i.e. no deaths or even close calls.)  I have gained 2.5 bubs in about 3 hours solo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzorryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zorryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#333333>(10/16/00 5:41:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt on Kunark?</span><hr size=1> I have moved to The Overthere zone to solo along the North shore.  This is working well.  At level 22, most of the mobs I ran into by the Windmills were either green, lowest blue, or yellow.  The Overthere seems to be a better hunting ground right now.<br>
<br>
-Zor<br>
Level 22 Mage <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzorryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zorryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#333333>(10/17/00 10:13:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt on Kunark?</span><hr size=1> Made 23 in The Overthere and too many greens were showing up so I moved.  I was looking in Warslik Woods and checked out the skulking brutes at the entrance to Dalnir.  I found that they were high blue, white, and yellow.  I had heard that their aggro radius was small so I solo'd a room of three of them.  The High blues are easy, the whites are tough, and the yellows are a challenge.  I usually spend 80% mana and 60% hp on the yellows. Anyway, this seems to be a good spot that could solo someone into the high 20s.<br>
<br>
Note: the brutes are on a 3min spawn which is perfect in a room of 15, you kill one every 5mins.<br>
<br>
-Zorryn level 23 Mage, Terris Thule <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzorryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zorryn</A> at: 10/17/00 4:17:25 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usatiini.showPublicProfile?language=EN>satiini</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.merikoski.edu.ouka.fi/~satiini/seven.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(9/17/01 6:07:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where to hunt on Kunark?</span><hr size=1> Overthere northcoast is definetly the way to go. No one EVER hunts here, very good spot. Guards are kinda near, merchants and banks near. Rhinos drop rhino horns (worth about 2pp) and they range from 16 all the way to 25, and only Sarnaks attack everything on sight. And theyre the only ones which give faction, so no bad faction here. <p><font color="#800080"><br>
